      "SummaryText": "\"Polyurethane Division of the Society of the Plastics Industry, Inc.\" provided resource information.  We discussed this program with the Cook County - North Local Emergency Planning Committee on June 21, 2001 and the Elgin Fire Department on May 30, 2001. Representatives of the Elgin Fire Department visited this plant on May 30, 2001. \n\n7. Planned changes to improve safety.\n\nThis facility was constructed in 2000 -2001 and is in compliance with all building and construction codes as indicated in section # 4.   No improvements are planned."
